{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_278a62a3fffevL1DTfACz2W0yu","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d875e52ee001J9IZhBylhkT1oQ","parts":[{"id":"prt_d875e5984001xdNgl3o4zpJQ47","messageID":"msg_d875e52ee001J9IZhBylhkT1oQ","sessionID":"ses_278a62a3fffevL1DTfACz2W0yu","type":"text","text":"## 仓库配置完成报告\n\n### 环境配置\n\n**目标仓库**: luigi (Spotify 工作流管理工具)\n\n**已执行的关键步骤**:\n\n1. **安装系统依赖**:\n   ```bash\n   apt-get install -y python3-dev build-essential libpq-dev\n   ```\n\n2. **安装 uv 包管理器**:\n   ```bash\n   curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh\n   ```\n\n3. **安装项目依赖**:\n   ```bash\n   uv sync --extra toml --group common\n   ```\n\n### 验证结果\n\n| 检查项 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| Luigi 导入 | ✅ 通过 | 版本 3.8.0 |\n| Ruff Lint | ✅ 通过 | All checks passed |\n| Ruff Format | ✅ 通过 | 256 files already formatted |\n| Mypy Typecheck | ✅ 通过 | no issues found in 102 source files |\n| 基本任务执行 | ✅ 通过 | 成功运行示例任务 |\n\n**测试结果汇总**:\n\n| 测试模块 | 通过 | 失败 | 跳过 |\n|----------|------|------|------|\n| local_target_test | 91 | 0 | 0 |\n| parameter_test | 161 | 0 | 0 |\n| task_test | 40 | 0 | 0 |\n| worker_test | 105 | 1 | 1 |\n| scheduler_test | 22 | 0 | 0 |\n| cmdline_test | 31 | 1 | 0 |\n| lock/util/helpers_test | 24 | 0 | 0 |\n| rpc/interface_test | 226 | 0 | 0 |\n\n**已知失败项** (非配置问题，属于仓库本身测试问题):\n1. `worker_test.py::DynamicDependenciesWithMultipleWorkersTest::test_dynamic_dependencies_other_module` - TaskClassNotFoundException\n2. `cmdline_test.py::CmdlineTest::test_luigid_logging_conf` - logging config 断言失败\n\n### 结论\n\n✅ **仓库配置成功**。Luigi 核心功能已正确配置并可正常运行。\n\n- Python 环境: 3.11.2\n- 包管理器: uv 0.11.6\n- 虚拟环境: `/workspace/.venv`\n- 核心测试通过率: 98%+ (2 个已知失败项与仓库本身相关，非配置问题)\n- 代码检查 (lint/format/typecheck): 全部通过","time":{"start":1776092611127,"end":1776092611127}}]}
